Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AngekreuztSpeechlet
    Angekreuzt Speechlet is used by Main, which is a SpeechletRequestStreamHandler.
    ArbeitundSoziales
    The public class ArbeitundSoziales collects information on the parties' views on employement and social life as described in the URL "http://www.bundestagswahl-bw.de/arbeit_soziales_btwahl2017.html".
    Bildung
    The public class Bildung collects information on the parties' views on education as described in the URL "http://www.bundestagswahl-bw.de/bildung_btwahl2017.html".
    Delegate
    Delegate is used for String retrieving and manipulation
    Erststimme
    accesses remote json data at abgeordnetenwatch.de or local for retrieving information about the candidates of a parliament.
    EUundAussenpolitik
    The public class EUundAussenpolitik collects information on the parties' views on the European Union and foreign affairs as described in the URL "http://www.bundestagswahl-bw.de/eu_aussenpolitik_btwahl2017.html".
    GroupMapping
    GroupMapping is used for Mapping of String Category to String group and from String Group to ArrayList of Strings of Categorys.
    IntegrationundAsyl
    The public class IntegrationundAsyl collects information on the parties' views on immigration and refugees as described in the URL "http://www.bundestagswahl-bw.de/integration_asyl_btwahl2017.html".
    Klient
    accesses remote json data at abgeordnetenwatch.de for retrieving answer to a political category.
    Main
    Main class is the responsible SpeechletRequestStreamHandler for an Alexa Skill
    Sicherheit
    The public class Sicherheit collects information on the parties' views on security as described in the URL "http://www.bundestagswahl-bw.de/sicherheit_btwahl2017.html".
    SpeechHelper
    Speechhelper has methods wrapInSpeak, interpretAs and createBreak for Alexa ssml speech
    SteuernundFinanzen
    The public class SteuernundFinanzen collects information on the parties' views on taxes and finances as described in the URL "http://www.bundestagswahl-bw.de/steuern_finanzen_btwahl2017.html".
    Themen
    Themen creates a Group mapping of ArrayList of Strings.
    Wahlsystem
    The public class Wahlsystem collects information on the election process in Germany as described in URL "http://www.bundestagswahl-bw.de/wahlsystem_btw.html" by using the Jsoup package.
    ZweitStimme
    This public class is used to determine the party's opinion concerning a political category.
